data.description: Desirable 3 Bedroom Home in the San Lucas Community offers custom designs through out. Stainless Steel Appliances, Granite Counter Tops, Pantry Closet, Custom Lighting under Cabinets & Much More. Open Kitchen Concept allows for Entertainment between Dinning & Main Area. Split floor plan providing private entrance to Primary Room. Extended Permitted Patio w/ built in Misters. Along w/ Flat Screen TV & Natural Wood Shelving perfect for BBQ's and enjoying the natural views. San Lucas Community offers parks throughout, walking paths w/ exercise equipment, community events all within the feel of private living. INSIDE TV/MOUNTS DO NOT CONVEY, NOR DOES THE 50 AMP ON SIDE OF HOME.
